relation: The identifier for the port channel. Enter an integer between 1 and 256. This ID cannot be changed after the port channel has been saved.

A user-defined name for the port channel. This name can be between 1 and 16 alphanumeric characters. You cannot use spaces or any special characters, and you cannot change this name after the object has been saved.
